The paper discusses the development of an open-source application for analyzing and visualizing machine learning systems, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The tool also allows for the measurement of fairness metrics, which could fall under the categories of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and cybersecurity (cs.CY). Additionally, the tool's focus on practical usage and minimal coding suggests a potential fit for software engineering (cs.SE).
